After Carl has logged into a SmartCloud Meeting as a Host, what are some features that he
can use during the meeting?
A. Raise my hand, sharing, and recording
B. Raise my hand, sharing and lock conference
C. Lock conference, sharing and polling
D. Lock conference, sharing and recording
Answer: A

A. SmartCloud Meetings and SmartCloud Notes
B. SmartCloud Meetings and SmartCloud Activities
C. SmartCloud iNotes and SmartCloud Communities
D. SmartCloud iNotes and SmartCloud Meetings
Answer: B
